Inspired by Technous Japan's game "Nekketsu Koukou Dodgeball Bu: Soccer Hen".

Based on retrogamelib (http://code.google.com/p/retrogamelib/) for screen and dialogs. 

Sounds from Eat the Whistle (http://etw.sourceforge.net/),
and SuperTuxKart (http://supertuxkart.sf.net).

For any question or help offer, write to: jmimu*AT*free.fr

How to play:
  P1: arrows (to move) + K (to kick, attack or ask to shoot), L (to pass or ask pass), P (for pause)
  P2: F, G, H (to move) +  A (to kick, attack or ask to shoot), Z (to pass or ask pass), R (for pause)


The configuration is given in config.txt file.
Its synthax is :
"""
#variable1
value
#variable2
value
...
"""
Variable name can be found in data/menus.xml.

